[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    135[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe three-layer architecture (rules → content-based candidate generation → personalization re-ranker) is the correct shape for a small, curated catalog with sparse engagement signal. Layer 1 as correctness and Layers 2-3 as optimization is the right framing.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    136[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Hard filters applied BEFORE candidate generation (language, audience, status). Same correct ordering as 4.1's eligibility filter.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    137[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The "candidate generator vs re-ranker" emphasis ("a dazzling re-ranker on top of a clueless candidate generator is still a clueless recommender") will save readers from the most common failure mode: tuning the re-ranker on a candidate set that's already wrong.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    138[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m "Curated vs. open catalog" is correctly identified as the property that makes this use case forgiving (no fake reviews, no SEO gaming, all items clinically reviewed) and the implications for technique selection are drawn correctly.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    139[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Embedding-model versioning is called out as a multi-month migration in the production-gaps section, including the parallel-index pattern.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    140[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Cold-start handling is honest: the recipe doesn't promise per-patient personalization for first-touch patients, and explicitly recommends an onboarding survey to bootstrap explicit signals.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    141[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Position-bias correction is called out in the production-gaps section. This is one of the most-missed details in production rankers.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    142[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m "Spend the first quarter on content metadata quality, then build the recommender" is the kind of opinion that comes from having watched a team flip the order. Worth its weight.[K
