[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    220[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Lambda layers cap at 250 MB unzipped (function + all layers combined). XGBoost wheel + numpy + scipy + the model artifact itself can be 100-150 MB depending on platform; a LightGBM model with all its deps lands in the same range. For a small starter ranker this works, but as the recipe predicts the team will eventually graduate to a learned ranker with more features, the layer ceiling becomes a real constraint sooner than readers expect.[K
