[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    11[0m:[38;5;10m[49m This is the seventh recipe in Chapter 11 (Conversational AI / Virtual Assistants) and the chapter's first longitudinal-coaching recipe. It is the chapter's first recipe to combine multi-year patient memory, structured care-plan-as-code, biometric-data ingestion with clinical thresholds, behavior-change-stage tracking with conversation-style adaptation, proactive engagement scheduling with attrition-mitigation discipline, citation-grounded longitudinal recommendations, mandatory-reporting routing for sensitive disclosures during multi-year coaching relationships, FDA-SaMD-strategy alignment for patient-facing chronic-disease management software, multi-window outcome correlation as a multi-quarter post-launch commitment, hybrid AI-plus-human coaching as the dominant production pattern, and care-team-workflow integration as a launch-day prerequisite. It establishes the chapter's chronic-coaching disciplines (care-plan-template library with clinical-specialty-leadership ownership per condition, longitudinal-store-as-architectural-primitive, biometric-data-integration with care-plan-specified thresholds, engagement-policy enforcement with patient-controlled opt-out granularity, behavior-change-stage tracking with motivational-interviewing pattern adaptation, citation-grounding as architectural floor with launch-gate threshold, continuous-emergency-screening on every utterance preserved from 11.6, sensitive-disclosure routing for IPV/substance-use/food-insecurity/medication-discontinuation/mental-health-crisis, multi-condition-integrated coaching as architecturally harder but more clinically valuable variant, outcome-correlation pipeline pulling subsequent encounter records and lab results and prescription fills and patient-reported outcomes, FDA SaMD-strategy artifact maintenance, hybrid AI-plus-human coaching with care-management integration, equity-monitoring as launch-gate-disparity-flagging) and frames the chapter's posture toward longitudinal patient-facing coaching tools as multi-year-relationship-quality engineering plus clinical-content-engineering plus regulatory-strategy-engineering that happens to use conversational AI rather than as conversational AI products that happen to maintain longitudinal memory.
