[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    15[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The Technology section is the chapter's introductory pedagogy on longitudinal-coaching-as-remember-engage-and-coach with multi-year-relationship-quality engineering and executes at the right grain. The "Why Chronic Disease Management Has Resisted Digital Tools For Twenty Years" subsection grounds the track-and-display-without-conversation and the curated-content-with-engagement-attrition failure modes in specific architectural diagnoses, with the references to Greenwood et al. 2017, Veazie et al. 2018, Sepah et al. 2017, Berman et al. 2018, and the Livongo/Omada/Virta/Vida vendor space appropriately TODO-hedged. The "What a Chronic Disease Coach Actually Does" subsection's nine-task-surface decomposition (onboarding and care-plan introduction, scheduled check-ins, patient-initiated conversations, biometric-data-triggered conversations, care-plan-milestone conversations, education and content delivery, behavior-change support, early-warning escalation, long-term relationship maintenance, care-team reporting) is correctly granular and recipe-distinct. The "Why a Generic LLM Cannot Run a Chronic Disease Coach" subsection's twelve-property enumeration is recipe-distinct and earns its position as the recipe's clearest articulation of the why-naked-LLM-in-front-of-longitudinal-coaching-is-not-a-coach primitive. The "What the Coach Has To Do That the Previous Bots Did Not" subsection's nine-structural-commitments enumeration (longitudinal patient memory as architectural primitive, care-plan-as-code with clinical-leadership ownership, biometric-data ingestion with clinical thresholds, engagement scheduler with policy-driven cadence, behavior-change-stage tracking with conversation-style adaptation, escalation taxonomy with care-plan-specified criteria, care-team reporting and longitudinal summarization, outcome-correlation pipeline as core post-launch commitment, FDA-strategy alignment as architectural constraint) is the recipe's clearest articulation of the chronic-coach-vs-other-chapter-11-bots-distinction primitive. The "Chronic-Coach Reality" subsection's twelve-property enumeration is the recipe's most-distinctive contribution.
