[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    191[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   1. **A successful prompt-injection on a coaching-tool-LLM produces multi-year-relationship-quality and patient-safety consequences.** A malicious utterance that triggers the care_plan_retrieve tool to retrieve a different patient's care plan (via patient_id manipulation), or a successful injection on the biometric_data_retrieve tool that returns data from a different patient, or a successful injection on the behavior_change_stage_update tool that sets the patient's stage incorrectly, or a successful injection on the escalation_propose tool that suppresses an escalation alert, or a successful injection on the care_team_alert_propose tool that suppresses a care-team alert, all produce coaching-decision-quality issues that propagate into the coaching-decision-record-journal as durable incorrect-coaching-decisions and may cause direct patient harm during an established multi-year relationship.
