[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    647[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Recipe 11.7 is publishable at the complex-regulated tier level once the three HIGH findings are closed. The Honest Take is the recipe's strongest single passage and the chapter's strongest single articulation of the clinical-and-relationship-quality-engineering-outweighs-the-ML-engineering primitive in multi-year-longitudinal-coaching context. The "Build the institutional muscles for the harder parts first; the coach is the easier part" framing matches the chapter pattern from 11.1, 11.2, 11.3, 11.4, 11.5, and 11.6 while elevating the recipe-distinct chronic-coach contributions.
