[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    649[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The recipe-specific contributions that should be elevated to the chapter preface as load-bearing primitives are: (a) the **longitudinal-patient-memory-as-architectural-primitive primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing for any multi-year-longitudinal-relationship recipe; the longitudinal store is the architectural primitive that distinguishes the coach from chatbots); (b) the **care-plan-as-code-with-clinical-specialty-leadership-ownership-per-condition primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; the care-plan-template library is the bot's clinical-safety ceiling and is owned by the appropriate clinical-specialty leadership per condition); (c) the **biometric-data-ingestion-with-care-plan-specified-thresholds primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; the thresholds are clinical-care-plan inputs signed by the patient's clinical team, not LLM choices); (d) the **engagement-scheduler-with-policy-driven-cadence-and-opt-out-granularity primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; engagement attrition is the central operational risk and engagement-policy enforcement is the institution's mitigation lever); (e) the **behavior-change-stage-tracking-with-conversation-style-adaptation primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; pre-contemplation-contemplation-preparation-action-maintenance demands different conversation styles); (f) the **continuous-emergency-screening-on-every-utterance-during-coaching primitive** (preserved from 11.6, recipe-acute amplified for chronic-condition-specific high-acuity patterns); (g) the **citation-grounding-as-launch-gate-with-care-plan-and-guideline-and-education-content primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing); (h) the **FDA-SaMD-strategy-artifact-as-versioned-regulatory-asset primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; patient-facing chronic-disease management software approaches the SaMD line); (i) the **care-team-reporting-and-longitudinal-summarization-as-first-class-capability primit